# Evaluator Deploy

Commit, push, and deploy the trader_evaluator project.

## Pre-flight

```bash
make test    # runs cargo test + clippy + fmt + skills-sync
```

All must pass. Never commit with failures.

## Commit and Push

```bash
git add <specific-files>
git commit -m "feat/fix/chore: description"
git push origin main
```

Commit BEFORE deploying. Never commit `.env`, `data/`, or credentials.

## Deploy (only for code/config changes)

```bash
make deploy
```

Server is resolved via `scripts/find_server.sh` (reads `deploy/.server-info`). Override when needed: `make deploy SERVER=ksonny@x.x.x.x` or `TRADING_SERVER_IP=x.x.x.x make deploy`.

This cross-compiles musl, SCPs to `/opt/evaluator/`, restarts systemd service, runs `make check`.

**Skip deploy for:** docs, skills, .cursor rules, README changes.

If the dashboard is behind a reverse proxy (cloudflared, nginx, ALB, etc.), the proxy must forward the `Cookie` and `Host` headers so login and CSRF work.

## Post-deploy Checks

```bash
# Service alive
ssh $(./scripts/find_server.sh) 'systemctl is-active evaluator'

# Metrics on port 9094
ssh $(./scripts/find_server.sh) 'curl -s localhost:9094/metrics | head -5'

# No panics
ssh $(./scripts/find_server.sh) 'journalctl -u evaluator --no-pager -n 20'

# Phase checks (run highest applicable; uses auto-discovered SERVER)
make check-phase-0   # Tables exist
make check-phase-1   # Markets scored
make check-phase-2   # Wallets classified
make check-phase-3   # Ingestion running
make check-phase-4   # Paper trading
make check-phase-5   # Wallet scores

# Pipeline overview
make status
```

